---
import PlayfulLayout from '../layouts/PlayfulLayout.astro';
import QuizMultiPage from '../components/QuizMultiPage.jsx';
import HomeButton from '../components/HomeButton.astro';

const title = 'Cybersecurity Quizzes: Test Your Skills | HackProof';
const description = 'Put your knowledge to the test with interactive quizzes on malware, phishing, cryptography, and network security. Instant feedback, no account needed.';
---
<PlayfulLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <HomeButton />

  <section style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto 24px;text-align:left;">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center;">Test What You've Learned</h2>
    <p>These quizzes cover the same four topics as the learning modules: malware, phishing, cryptography, and network security, plus a final mixed round that pulls questions from all of them. Each question includes real-world scenarios, like a suspicious popup or a banking email, so you're practicing the kind of judgment calls you'll actually face online.</p>
    <p>Answer at your own pace and get instant feedback on each question, including an explanation of why an answer is right or wrong. No account or signup is required. Just pick a section below and start testing your skills.</p>
  </section>

  <QuizMultiPage client:load />
</PlayfulLayout>